Subject: [PATCH v2 2/3] bus: mhi: core: Introduce debugfs entries for MHI
Date:   Fri, 18 Sep 2020 12:26:52 -0700
Message-Id: <1600457213-11587-3-git-send-email-bbhatt@codeaurora.org>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.7.4
In-Reply-To: <1600457213-11587-1-git-send-email-bbhatt@codeaurora.org>
References: <1600457213-11587-1-git-send-email-bbhatt@codeaurora.org>
Precedence: bulk
List-ID: <linux-kernel.vger.kernel.org>
X-Mailing-List: linux-kernel@vger.kernel.org

Introduce debugfs entries to show state, register, channel, device,
and event rings information. Allow the host to dump registers,
issue device wake, and change the MHI timeout to help in debug.

Signed-off-by: Bhaumik Bhatt <bbhatt@codeaurora.org>
